F4A-9 — List Staged Apps
Inside Prior Gates Incomplete → If No, after Loop Staged CPs. Dataverse → List rows.
Table: Staged Records
Filter rows: fx → concat('_pei_importcycle_value eq ', variables('varImportCycleID'), ' and pei_entitytype eq 890920001')
Rename to: List Staged Apps

F4A-10 — Loop Staged Apps
Apply to each, after List Staged Apps.
Select output: fx → outputs('List_Staged_Apps')?['body/value']
Rename to: Loop Staged Apps

F4A-11 — Find App Record
Inside Loop Staged Apps. Dataverse → List rows.
Table: Applications
Filter rows: fx → concat('pei_displayname eq ''', items('Loop_Staged_Apps')?['pei_name'], '''')
Rename to: Find App Record
Note: App match key is pei_displayname, not pei_leanixapplicationid — same reason as Flow 1 (LeanIX ID fails at runtime).

F4A-12 — Condition: App Found
Inside Loop Staged Apps, after Find App Record.
Left: fx → length(outputs('Find_App_Record')?['body/value'])
Operator: is greater than
Right: 0
Rename to: App Found

F4A-13 — Update App Reviewed
Inside App Found → If Yes. Dataverse → Update a row.
Table name: Applications
Row ID: lightning bolt → expand "Find App Record" → select Application (the GUID dynamic content)
Reviewed: Yes (dropdown — boolean)
Leave every other field blank.
Rename to: Update App Reviewed
